definitions.definition: Data that describes other data, serving as an informative label .
examples: Most websites contain metadata to tell the computer how to lay out the content on the screen.

definitions.definition: Structured information about a file (date created, creator, software used to create, last modified, file format, file fingerprint, etc).
examples: That photo's metadata suggests it was edited using Photoshop.

main_definition: Data that describes other data, serving as an informative label .
